Policy.acknowledgement_statement: This work was supported by the following grants: Genomic Predictors of Arteriosclerosis in Hypertensives Study - (STAMPEED) R01 HL087660 Genetic Determinants of High Blood Pressure in Three Racial Groups - (GENOA) U01 HL054457 The Family Blood Pressure Program (FPBB) - U01 HL054481 The Epidemiology of CAC Study (ECAC) - R01 HL46292 Biomarkers of Peripheral Arterial Disease - R01 HL075794 Genetics of Microangiopathic Brain Injury (GMBI) - R01 NS041558 We would like to thank the GENOA participants and the GENOA Research Group for their valuable contribution to this research.
Policy.ic_specific_access_term: Use of the data is limited only by the terms of the model Data Use Certification. This dataset only contains summary-level results. For access to individual-level phenotype and genotype data please request access to Genetic Epidemiology Network of Arteriopathy (GENOA) dbGaP Study Accession: phs001238.
